headline: Verisk to Announce Fiscal Fourth-Quarter 2025 and Full-Year 2025 Results on February 18, 2026
summary: JERSEY CITY, N.J., Jan. 21, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Verisk (Nasdaq: VRSK), a leading strategic data analytics and technology partner to the global insurance industry, will report its financial results for the fourth quarter and fiscal year ended December 31, 2025, on Wednesday, February 18, 2026, before the market open. headline: Verisk Analytics' Q4 2025 Earnings: What to Expect
summary: Verisk Analytics will release its fourth-quarter earnings soon, and analysts anticipate a low single-digit profit dip.
